<p/>
<p><hi rend="underline">Points to be attended</hi> to: relative heights of pistil &amp; stamens—of corolla &amp; calyx; &amp; of the <hi rend="underline">enlargement</hi> of corolla, where anthers are situated.—</p> 
<figure type="diagram"> 
<p>(Longitudinal Section of) (<hi rend="underline">Common Primrose</hi>)–</p> </figure> 
<p>(Longitudinal Section of <hi rend="underline">Common Primrose</hi>)— Clean, hard outlines for 2 woodcuts, matching in size &amp; to stand near alongside each other.<ref target="#foot.f5"/></p>
<p>Corolla &amp; calyx of same length in the two</p> 
                </div>
        
